public class Main
{
	public static void main(String[] args) {
	    int A=5*2-8;
	    int B=7/4+4*7;
		System.out.println("value of A: "+A);
		System.out.println("value of B: "+B);
	}
}

Explaination of order of operation

operation steps of A.

step-1: 5*2=10
step-2: 10-8=2
valueof A: 2

operation steps of B.

step-1: 7/4=1
step-2: 4*7=28
step-3: 1+28=29
valueof B: 29
